## Additional Software Installation

### OpenRefine

![OpenRefine и другие альтернативные MS Excel инструменты нормализации справочников для Экспертов ...](https://external-content.duckduckgo.com/iu/?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhabrastorage.org%2Fgetpro%2Fhabr%2Fupload_files%2F0af%2Fc41%2F728%2F0afc41728d2c4850d84f0199dd32a15d.png&f=1&nofb=1&ipt=805de5e5751728778815f7bc53366da0608a8fe233bf16cc90cba9dfb83b723a)

OpenRefine is essential for data cleaning and transformation:

**Installation:**

1. Visit [openrefine.org](https://openrefine.org)
2. Download the appropriate version for your OS
3. Extract the downloaded file
4. Launch according to your operating system instructions
5. Verify by opening localhost:3333 in your browser

![](images/20260224_095544_image.png)

**Usage Notes:**

- OpenRefine runs as a local web application
- Keep the terminal/command window open while using
- Works with CSV, JSON, XML, and other structured data formats

### Secure FTP Client

For transferring files to Stanford's AFS system:

**SecureFX (Cross-platform):**

1. Read about your AFS Web Hosting Space at: [https://uit.stanford.edu/service/web/centralhosting/howto_user](https://uit.stanford.edu/service/web/centralhosting/howto_user)
2. Install SecureFX using default settings
3. Configure connection to `cardinal.stanford.edu`
4. Test connection with your Stanford credentials

![](images/20260224_095829_image.png)

**SecureFX FTP Client Stanford UIT Installation Instructions:**

- **Windows:** SecureFX: [https://uit.stanford.edu/service/ess/scrt_sfx/securefx](https://uit.stanford.edu/service/ess/scrt_sfx/securefx)
- **macOS:** SecureFX: [https://uit.stanford.edu/service/ess/scrt_sfx/securefx/mac/install](https://uit.stanford.edu/service/ess/scrt_sfx/securefx/mac/install)

### Text Editor


![](images/20260224_112727_image.png)

A good text editor is essential for code and documentation. I'm writing this entire Github Book, using Visual Studio Code, which I like for all of it's integrations and plugin ecosystem:

**Recommended Options:**

- [Visual Studio Code](https://code.visualstudio.com/download) Free, cross-platform, excellent for code.
- [Sublime Text](https://www.sublimetext.com/) : Simple, clean interface. Good for those intimidated by VSC.
